                                </name>
                            </author>
                            <title xml:lang="eng" type="desc">Commentary on Hippocratic
                                Aphorisms</title>
                            <title xml:lang="ara">شرح فصول أبقراط</title>
                            <title xml:lang="eng" type="alt">Sharḥ Fuṣūl Abuqrāṭ</title>
                            <note> This is a lemmatically arranged commentary. The introduction begins on <locus>f. 2b</locus>; the beginning of each Book is as follows:
